arts.ttl: Feyenoord 2-3 PSV: Records rife as PSV keep title dream alive
arts.sum: Feyenoord surrendered a two-goal lead to lose 2-3 late on against PSV at De Kuip, giving the visitors newfound title dreams as Ajax also lost.
